// Tracked, secret-free signing config referenced by project.yml (configFiles).
//
// It must stay in the repo so `xcodegen generate` (and CI) always finds it — but it holds NO
// team id itself, so nothing personal is baked into the tracked Cotabby.xcodeproj.
//
// Your personal Apple Development Team goes in `LocalTeam.xcconfig` (gitignored). Xcode follows
// the optional include below at BUILD time, so signing works locally without rewriting the
// shared project. Setup: `cp LocalTeam.xcconfig.example LocalTeam.xcconfig` and set your id.
#include? "LocalTeam.xcconfig"
